---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../site.config';
---

<Base title="About" description={site.meta.about}>
  <p class="prompt-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> cat about.md</p>
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Hi, I’m Alex! Born and raised in Northern Virginia, I started my journey at
    Northern Virginia Community College (NOVA) before serving in the Army Reserves.
    Today, I work in the tech sector, specializing in government-focused projects.
    I am currently expanding beyond core operational work to build scalable personal
    projects and independent software ventures.
  </p>

  <p>
    Outside of work, my weekends are fueled by movement and exploration. I’m a dedicated
    runner, using long runs to discover new trails locally and short runs to scout new
    cities whenever I travel. When I’m not running or at the bouldering gym, I’m usually
    tracking down a great cup of coffee (with Brooklyn's Nilis holding the top spot), or
    out with my camera capturing landscapes and historic architecture. The rest of my time
    is all about winding down with my fiancée!
  </p>

  <p>
    P.S. I hate writing, so AI has definitely helped write a lot of this. By far
    my biggest weakness.
  </p>

  <h2>Now</h2>
  <ul class="now-list">
    <li><span class="now-key">reading</span> <span class="now-val">The Catcher in the Rye</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">building</span> <span class="now-val">This website</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">learning</span> <span class="now-val">Go, slowly</span></li>
    <li><span class="now-key">listening</span> <span class="now-val">Homewrecker</span></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
  <ul class="elsewhere">
    <li><a href={site.social.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github</a></li>
    <li><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>email</a></li>
  </ul>
</Base>

<style>
  .prompt-line {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  h1 { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .lede { max-width: 60ch; }
  p { max-width: 60ch; }

  .now-list, .elsewhere {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .now-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border-muted);
  }

  .now-key {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    min-width: 6rem;
  }

  .now-val {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .elsewhere {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
